<br>
Another idea I certainly chucked around when I think about EQ in my spare time was the idea of not just a merchant guild, but also within that guild, people who are good at certain tradeskills.<br>
<br>
What basically the guild is this:<br>
<br>
Lets call it the Traders of Norrath...so you have some tinkerers...some jewellers..but the whole guild is self sufficient. The guild lives off the profit it generates through tradeskills and using mains to obtain ingredients.<br>
<br>
Just a thought..<br>
