If you want to verify that mules belong to particular mains, you could require that everyone be signed up at <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://eq.guildmagic.com">eq.guildmagic.com</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> which allows you to see which other characters belong to someone. Of course, a scammer could create a fake account, but since many guilds and individuals already use it they may well find their intended victims name already taken by the real owner.<br>
